data.description: This beautiful HORSE RANCH on just over 10 ACRES is waiting for you to enjoy NATURE in the middle of the WITHLACOOCHEE STATE FOREST.  Bring the HORSES because there is plenty of ROOM for ROAMING and TRAINING on this massive FULLY FENCED 10 acre ESTATE.  The main home has 3 BR, 2BA with nearly 1,700sf of space that OPENS to a WRAP-AROUND PORCH. Enjoy the beautiful BREEZE while riding through the FOREST!  The property also includes a CENTER AISLE PROFESSIONAL BARN with 8 STALLS, FEED ROOM, TACK ROOM. You will LOVE living RURAL with the conveniences of shopping, restaurants, hospitals and so much more in Brooksville and Inverness being so close!  MOTIVATED SELLER, so call NOW for a PRIVATE SHOWING TODAY!!!
